WEBVTT

00:10:24.221 --> 00:10:30.077
I still feel very strongly
that digital connectivity,

00:10:30.101 --> 00:10:33.196
which is -- people may be losing
sight of the fact --

00:10:33.220 --> 00:10:35.704
it is enabling very positive things,

00:10:35.728 --> 00:10:37.149
it's still a very good thing,

00:10:37.173 --> 00:10:40.481
but the idea of how we take --

00:10:40.505 --> 00:10:42.110
OK, it can be used for bullying,

00:10:42.134 --> 00:10:45.410
or political persuasion
that we think is inappropriate.

00:10:45.434 --> 00:10:47.574
We need some invention here.

00:10:47.598 --> 00:10:49.404
When I sit and talk with critics,

00:10:49.428 --> 00:10:51.170
I say, "OK, what is your solution?"

00:10:51.194 --> 00:10:55.535
In many cases, they're
much better at criticizing,

00:10:55.559 --> 00:10:57.529
saying, "OK, there's a filter bubble,"

00:10:57.553 --> 00:11:02.704
but absent getting rid of human freedom
to choose what you read online,